# cohort-accessibility-auditor Sub-agent

> Source: `~/Development/cohort/.claude/agents/cohort-accessibility-auditor.md`

## Activation
UI commit PR + landing/waitlist/onboarding surface.

## WCAG 2.1 AA 8-dimension audit
1. **Color contrast**: text 4.5:1 (normal) / 3:1 (large) — vault 42 §2.1 ink scale verify
2. **Touch target**: 44×44px+ minimum (AD-2)
3. **Focus state**: focus-visible:outline + 2px offset
4. **Semantic HTML**: heading hierarchy + landmarks + form labels
5. **Keyboard navigation**: Tab order + Enter activation + Escape close
6. **Screen reader**: aria-label + aria-describedby + role
7. **Reduced motion**: prefers-reduced-motion respect (AD-6)
8. **Color-blindness**: 색 정보 영역 non-color signal 영역 redundant 의무

## Output
- `✓ cohort-accessibility-auditor PASS` + 8-dimension verdict
- 또는 `❌ {dimension} {detail}` + remediation suggestion
